\f0\fs24 \cf0 # Sojern Design System \'97 Cursor Reference\
\
## About this repo\
This is the Sojern component library. All screens and wireframes\
must be built using components and tokens from DesignSystem.jsx only.\
\
## Stack\
- React (JSX)\
- Inline styles using the tokens object \'97 no CSS files, no Tailwind\
- Fonts: Lato (titles) + Inter (body) \'97 load via Google Fonts\
\
## Rules \'97 always follow these\
- ALWAYS import components from ./components/DesignSystem.jsx\
- NEVER hardcode colors, spacing or font sizes \'97 always use tokens\
- NEVER create a new component if one already exists in DesignSystem.jsx\
- ALL new pages go in the /pages folder\
- ALWAYS use PageLayout as the wrapper for every new page\
- ALWAYS use the Sidebar component with the correct nav items\
- ALWAYS use Breadcrumb at the top of every page\
\
## Brand\
- Brand Primary (orange): #E35F3E \'97 used for CTAs, active states\
- Brand Secondary (dark navy): #242452 \'97 used for sidebar, headers\
- Brand Tertiary (steel blue): #647D94 \'97 used for hover states\
- Page background: #F8F8F8\
- Container background: #FFFFFF\
\
## Typography\
- Titles: Lato font\
- Body/UI: Inter font\
- Never use any other font\
\
## Available components\
Import any of these from DesignSystem.jsx:\
\
| Component | Usage |\
|---|---|\
| Button | variant: special, primary, secondary, ghost, destructive, link |\
| Chip | variant: warning, success, error, active, information |\
| Toast | variant: success, critical, warning, info |\
| Toggle | On/off switch |\
| Checkbox | Form checkbox with error state |\
| Radio | Form radio button with error state |\
| Breadcrumb | Page navigation trail |\
| Tabs | Horizontal tab navigation |\
| Tooltip | Hover tooltip, data or info variant |\
| FormInput | Text input, dropdown, with all states |\
| Modal | size: md, lg |\
| Sidebar | Expanded and collapsed states |\
| Table | With sorting, selection, chips |\
| Pagination | With rows per page selector |\
| Card | Metric display cards |\
| Stepper | Multi-step wizard progress |\
| PageLayout | Full page wrapper with sidebar |\
\
## Button variants\
- special = orange (#E35F3E) \'97 primary CTA\
- primary = dark navy (#26374E) \'97 secondary CTA  \
- secondary = white with navy border \'97 tertiary action\
- ghost = transparent \'97 low emphasis\
- destructive = red (#E02F2F) \'97 delete/remove actions\
- link = blue (#1362F7) \'97 inline links\
\
## Status colors\
- Success: #488F31 on #E2F9F1\
- Warning: #C86400 on #FEF7E3\
- Error: #E02F2F on #F9DFD8\
- Info: #005A9E on #CBE8FF\
- Neutral: #333333 on #E0E5EA\
\
## Table behaviour\
- Default sort: date column, descending (newest first)\
- Selected row background: #F5F1EE\
- Hover row background: #F8F8F8\
- Status column uses Chip component\
\
## Example prompt to use in Cursor\
"Using the components in DesignSystem.jsx and following\
the rules in CLAUDE.md, build me a [page name] page with\
[list the components you need]"}